From b44bc5bc3cd80c5f46c070aa94ac4bd552542b8b Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "copilot-swe-agent[bot]" <198982749+Copilot@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Sat, 30 May 2026 13:16:01 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] ath9k: add range check for conn_rsp_epid in
 htc_connect_service()

Backport upstream fix 8619593634cb:
  ath9k_htc: Do range check before using conn_rsp_epid

If conn_rsp_epid is out of range, it will cause array out of bounds.
Add a range check before assigning it to *conn_rsp_epid.
---
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath9k/htc_hst.c | 3 +++
 1 file changed, 3 insertions(+)

--- a/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath9k/htc_hst.c
+++ b/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath9k/htc_hst.c
@@ -297,6 +297,9 @@ int htc_connect_service(struct htc_targe
 		return -ETIMEDOUT;
 	}
 
+	if (target->conn_rsp_epid >= ENDPOINT_MAX)
+		return -EINVAL;
+
 	*conn_rsp_epid = target->conn_rsp_epid;
 	return 0;
 err:
